# ğŸ° Majestic Forts of Pune

A responsive and informative **frontend website** showcasing the historic forts around Pune, Maharashtra.  
This project highlights the **Maratha heritage**, famous forts, trekking information, and visitor guidance.

---

## âœ¨ Project Overview
The **Pune Forts Explorer** website is designed to educate and inspire users to explore the majestic forts built during the Maratha Empire.  
It presents historical significance, locations, trekking tips, and featured forts in a clean and modern UI.

---

## ğŸŒŸ Features
- Hero section with Maratha heritage theme
- Featured forts with images and descriptions
- Individual fort explore pages (Sinhgad, Lohagad, Purandar, etc.)
- Trekking & visitor guide section
- Historical and cultural information
- Responsive and user-friendly design
- Clean layout using pure HTML & CSS

